      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit delivers exceptional linear power delivery through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanical integrity has been prioritized: the Double VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe\u2014a known point of fatigue\u2014has been professionally reinforced to ensure chassis torsional rigidity. Power is efficiently transferred via a variable M-differential lock. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing factory-spec bushings to maintain communicative steering feedback. While the exterior shows minor road-patina consistent with its mileage, the high-revving drivetrain remains a benchmark for naturally aspirated performance. This is a mechanically sound example optimized for the purist.",
